{
  "text": "These theoretical models adopt some parameters, such as the coefficients for the reaction-kinetics rate, catalyst adsorption, etc., which are calculated using data fitting [CITATION_1] . These tools provide a clear system understanding, combined to a good generalization over a wide range of data, needing lower computational efforts than other theoretical models.",
